      <div class="container">
        <h1 id="forag">Forage</h1>
        <p>
          Foraging, etc. are -10 in Winter, +5 in Summer.  Heath,
          Alpine, Marsh, Shores, Cropland -5, Caverns -15, Woodland
          +5.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <h1 id="armour">Armour Prices</h1>
        <p>
	  Armour (base) prices are calculated as follows: From the
	  equipment name infer the areas covered and the material.
	  Take the coverage percentage and multiply by the base cost
	  and base weight.
        </p>
